

-   float top parent if children float and they are not in context space 
-   All elements have postion: static by default
-   display: inline will have effect of span where elements have no width or height 
             & does not start new line
-   display: block will take all the width and starts new line
-   box-sizing: border-box; (default is content-box) will keep border and padding within 
    height and width sizing rather than adding to it like content-box value would


